  <header id=\"header-area\">\r\n    <div class=\"logo-main\"><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/index.html\"><b><span class=\"sub\"></span><span class=\"main\">四国旅客鉄道株式会社</span></b><span>採用情報<br>総合TOP</span></a></div>\r\n    <div id=\"humberger\">\r\n      <div class=\"trigger\">\r\n        <span></span>\r\n        <span></span>\r\n        <span></span>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <nav id=\"navi-global-area\">\r\n      <ul class=\"navi-global\">\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/index.html\">経験者採用TOP</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/company/index.html\">会社を知る</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/works/index.html\">仕事を知る</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/human_resources/index.html\">社員を知る</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/working_environment/index.html\">働く環境</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/information/index.html\">採用情報</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/qa/index.html\">Q&amp;A</a></li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n\t\t<ul class=\"navi-entry oubo-career\">\r\n\t\t  <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/information/employ.html#oubo-career\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\">応募方法</a></li>\r\n\t\t</ul>\r\n    </nav>\r\n  </header>\r\n  <!--// HEADER -->\n  <div class=\"top-main-image\">\n  <div class=\"image-main\">\n    <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n      <figure class=\"swiper-slide image-main1\"></figure>\n      <figure class=\"swiper-slide image-main2\"></figure>\n      <figure class=\"swiper-slide image-main3\"></figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"top-main-head\">\n    <h1><img src=\"img/img_catch.svg\" alt=\"四国の未来を、あなたの手で。\"/></h1>\n  </div>\n</div>\n    <main>\n    <!--<section class=\"information-sec\">\n      <div class=\"information-sec-inner\">\n        <div class=\"information-list-wrap\">\n          <h2 class=\"en\">INFORMATION</h2>\n          <dl class=\"information-list\">\n            <div>\n              <dt class=\"en\"></dt>\n              <dd></dd>\n            </div>\n          </dl>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>-->\n    \n    <section class=\"company-sec sec\">\n      <div class=\"company-sec-inner\">\n        <div class=\"company-detail\">\n          <div class=\"heading-wrap\">\n            <p class=\"en\">COMPANY</p>\n            <h2 class=\"jp\">会社を知る</h2>\n          </div>\n          <p>ＪＲ四国が目指していることや、安全への取り組み、新しい分野への挑戦、プロジェクトなど、四国と共に歩むＪＲ四国の姿をご紹介します。</p>\n          <a href=\"company/index.html\" class=\"bt-viewmore en\">VIEW MORE</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    \n    <section class=\"works-sec sec\">\n      <div class=\"col1\">\n        <figure class=\"image wide\"></figure>\n        <figure class=\"image\"></figure>\n        <figure class=\"image\"></figure>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col2 works-detail\">\n        <div class=\"heading-wrap\">\n          <p class=\"en\">WORKS</p>\n          <h2 class=\"jp\">仕事を知る</h2>\n        </div>\n        <p>保線、土木、建築、車両・工場機械設備、<br class=\"pc-ver\">電気、事業開発など、四国の未来を創るための<br class=\"pc-ver\">幅広い仕事領域についてご紹介します。</p>\n        <a href=\"works/index.html\" class=\"bt-viewmore en\">VIEW MORE</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col3\">\n        <figure class=\"image\"></figure>\n        <figure class=\"image\"></figure>\n        <figure class=\"image wide\"></figure>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    \n    <section class=\"human-resources-sec sec\">\n      <div class=\"human-resources-detail-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"human-resources-detail\">\n          <div class=\"heading-wrap\">\n            <p class=\"en\">HUMAN <br class=\"sp-ver\">RESOURCES</p>\n            <h2 class=\"jp\">社員を知る</h2>\n          </div>\n          <p>それぞれの強みや個性を活かしながら、四国への想いをかたちにしていく。<br>ＪＲ四国で活躍する、経験者採用社員をご紹介します。</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"employee-list\">\n        <div class=\"swiper\">\n          <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"employee-list-item itokawa civil\">\n              <a href=\"human_resources/itokawa/index.html\">\n              <figure class=\"image\"></figure>\n              <div class=\"profile\">\n                <p class=\"joined jp\">2018年入社</p>\n                <p class=\"name en\">KAZUKI ITOKAWA</p>\n              </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"employee-list-item hirose development\">\n              <a href=\"human_resources/hirose/index.html\">\n              <figure class=\"image\"></figure>\n              <div class=\"profile\">\n                <p class=\"joined jp\">2022年入社</p>\n                <p class=\"name en\">FUMIATSU HIROSE</p>\n              </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"btn-area\">\n          <a href=\"human_resources/index.html\" class=\"bt-viewmore en\">VIEW MORE</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    \n    <section class=\"working-environment-sec sec\">\n      <div class=\"sec-inner\">\n        <figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"img/img_working.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n        <div class=\"detail\">\n          <div class=\"heading-wrap\">\n            <p class=\"en\">WORKING<br>ENVIRONMENT</p>\n            <h2 class=\"jp\">働く環境</h2>\n          </div>\n          <p>生き生きと働ける職場環境づくりや、社員の生活をバックアップする仕組み、成長を後押しする仕組みについてご紹介します。</p>\n          <a href=\"working_environment/index.html\" class=\"bt-viewmore en\">VIEW MORE</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    \n    <section class=\"recruit-sec sec\">\n      <div class=\"sec-inner\">\n        <figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"img/img_recruit.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n        <div class=\"detail\">\n          <div class=\"heading-wrap\">\n            <p class=\"en\">RECRUIT</p>\n            <h2 class=\"jp\">採用情報</h2>\n          </div>\n          <p>通年応募可能な経験者採用の募集要項についてご案内します。</p>\n          <a href=\"information/index.html\" class=\"bt-viewmore en\">VIEW MORE</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  \n  <section class=\"faq-sec sec\">\n      <div class=\"sec-inner\">\n        <figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"img/img_faq.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n        <div class=\"detail\">\n          <div class=\"heading-wrap\">\n            <p class=\"en\">Q&amp;A</p>\n            <h2 class=\"jp\">よくある質問</h2>\n          </div>\n          <p>勤務や待遇、配属、さらに選考など、様々な事項について、応募者の皆さんからよく寄せられる質問にお答えします。</p>\n          <a href=\"qa/index.html\" class=\"bt-viewmore en\">VIEW MORE</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    </main>\n    <!-- FOOTER -->\r\n<footer id=\"footer-area\">\r\n  <div class=\"footer-inner\">\r\n    <div class=\"footer-upper\">\r\n      <div class=\"footer-logo\"><img src=\"/04_company/recruit/common/img/logo_footer.png\" alt=\"四国旅客鉄道株式会社\"/>\r\n      <span>経験者<br>採用情報</span></div>\r\n      <ul class=\"footer-navi\">\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/company/index.html\">会社を知る</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/works/index.html\">仕事を知る</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/human_resources/index.html\">社員を知る</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/working_environment/index.html\">働く環境</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/information/index.html\">採用情報</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"/04_company/recruit/career/qa/index.html\">Q&amp;A</a></li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"footer-lower\">\r\n      <a href=\"https://www.jr-shikoku.co.jp/\" class=\"offcial\" target=\"_blank\">オフィシャルサイト</a>\r\n      <small class=\"copyright\">Copyright(C) Shikoku Railway Company. All rights reserved.</small>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</footer>\r\n<!--// FOOTER -->\n<script src=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js\" integrity=\"sha512-v2CJ7UaYy4JwqLDIrZUI/4hqeoQieOmAZNXBeQyjo21dadnwR+8ZaIJVT8EE2iyI61OV8e6M8PP2/4hpQINQ/g==\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"referrerpolicy=